  title="The Conversation Is Rarely the Problem"
  lead="Why good people on good teams keep misreading each other, and what to do about it."
  metaTitle="The Conversation Is Rarely the Problem — Ennea Evolution"
  metaDescription="Most workplace conflict isn't a communication problem. It's an interpretation problem. One question that catches the misread before it becomes the conflict."
  startHeading="This is the core of what I teach teams"
  start="How to catch the misread before it becomes the conflict."
  ctaLabel="See how it works for your team"
